		</ul>
		<div class="text-editor-wrap" data-wow-duration="5s">
			<div class="title-bar"><span class="title">about-me.js — bash — 80x<span class="terminal-height">25</span></span></div>
			<div class="text-body">
				$ <span id="typed"></span>
			</div>
